Class uppaalBaseListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • parsers.Declaration.ANTLRGenerated.uppaalBaseListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    uppaalListener
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DeclarationUpdater, SystemDeclParser, VariableInstantiationReader

    public class uppaalBaseListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements uppaalListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of uppaalListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
